lead_paragraph: Carlos Santana hit a three-run homer, Francisco Lindor added a two-run shot and the Cleveland Indians salvaged the finale of a four-game series with Minnesota 9-2 on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Indians Use Home Runs to Finally Defeat Twins 9-2
